# StepFold: A Progressive Local-to-Global Generation Framework for RNA Secondary Structure Prediction

[![DOI](https://zenodo.org/badge/DOI/10.5281/zenodo.19556209.svg)](https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.19556209)
[![License: CC BY 4.0](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-CC_BY_4.0-lightgrey.svg)](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)

This repository contains the official implementation for the paper: **"StepFold: A Progressive Local-to-Global Generation Framework for RNA Secondary Structure Prediction."**

